                                <date>1958</date>. С. <biblScope unit="page">??–??</biblScope>.</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><xi:include href="../encodingdesc.xml" parse="xml"/></teiHeader><text><body><entry xml:id="entry_ḱyrystī" xml:lang="os"><form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>ḱyrystī</orth></form><form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>kiriste</orth></form><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru"><q>Христос</q></abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en"><q>Christ</q></abv:tr></sense><re><form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>ḱyryston</orth></form><form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>kiriston</orth></form><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru"><q>христианин</q></abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en"><q>Christian</q></abv:tr></sense><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">; отмечена форма %iḱryston%i</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en">; the form %iḱryston%i is also attested</note></re><abv:exampleGrp><abv:example><quote>ḱryston læǵīmæ k˳yd kænʒynæ kajys?</quote><abv:tr xml:lang="ru"><q>как ты породнишься с христианином?</q></abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en"><q>How will you become related with a Christian?</q></abv:tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Коста"/><biblScope>143</biblScope></bibl></abv:example></abv:exampleGrp><etym xml:lang="ru">Из <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><lang/> <w>kriste</w></mentioned> (← <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><lang/> <w>Χριστός</w></mentioned>). Из грузинского идут и некоторые другие термины христианского культа; см. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ǵiorguba"/> и др.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">From <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><lang/> <w>kriste</w></mentioned> (← <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><lang/> <w>Χριστός</w></mentioned>). Some other terms of Christian cult come from Georgian; see <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ǵiorguba"/> etc.</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>